este campo.


7
00:02:42.004 --> 00:02:47.781
<b>IMPASSE</b>

8
00:02:51.917 --> 00:02:54.836
Samuel Greene
"O nosso tudo" 2008-2015


9
00:03:03.883 --> 00:03:07.397
